   Economy:
   Personal Income
   And Spending Rose
   In Latest Month
   ----
   By Katherine Walsh
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/29/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
